snippet.title: Valerio Velardo - The Sound of AI
snippet.description:
Hi there! I'm Valerio Velardo, an AI audio/music engineer and consultant with a PhD in Music & AI. In this channel, I publish tutorials on AI audio/music, I talk about cool AI music projects, and share my experience in the audiotech space. 

If you're interested in my consulting/freelancing services, please check out https://valeriovelardo.com/ 

Hope you stick around!
